{"tid":417161,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"【全台第一爆】iPhone 8充電中爆裂　嚇壞鐵粉","createTime":"2017-09-28T11:51:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-28T14:35:24.000Z","uid":46231,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9cf94acfec86b9ef9b770951fa79fbb43405897a","tid":417161,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:51:27.000Z","msg":"iPhone 8本月22日全球開賣，台灣首度傳出爆裂案例。台中一名吳姓女子向《蘋果》爆料，剛入手第三天的iPhone 8 Plus，手機外殼竟在充電時爆裂，嚇得她趕緊拔掉插頭，馬上連絡通訊行，初步懷疑是電池膨脹導致，通訊行已將手機收回，準備送回原廠檢視，當事人表示，好險立即發現，再充下去，搞不好會燒起來。<br />\n<br />\n投訴的吳姓女子表示，她是iPhone的鐵粉，23日向台中一家通訊行，以每月999元的月租價格方式續約，購買原廠價2萬8900元的iPhone 8 Plus金色，容量是64G，26日當天下午，手機電量還有百分之70，但想說等下要追劇看片，先插線充電一下，便外出送客人離開，只有3分鐘時間就回原位，一看手機竟已經爆開，但她並沒聽到任何爆裂聲響。吳小姐說，她從iPhone 4就開始使用迄今，就一般狀況使用iPhone，看看臉書、拍照、追劇等，沒有玩手遊，充電線等都是原廠的，也沒有摔到、凹折等，不明白為何會爆開？這次爆裂風波後，還是會繼續使用iPhone，畢竟已經習慣，在拿到新機之前，先暫用之前舊的iPhone 7，但心裡已經有陰影，很怕拿到手機又爆開。記者也到該通訊行找到爆裂的手機，發現手機外殼與螢幕明顯爆裂分家，裂縫約0.5公分，但外觀沒有外傷或凹折等，看起來是從內部爆開，而手機還是可以正常使用；通訊行已經連盒子打包好，準備送回原廠，張姓業者表示，iPhone 8已經賣了10幾支，這起應該算是個案，將另外給同款的手機給吳小姐。（田兆緯／台中報導）<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170928/1212655/?utm_source=FB&amp;utm_medium=MWeb_Share&amp;utm_campaign=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170928%2F1212655%2F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170928%2F1212655%2F%3Futm_source%3DFB%26utm_medium%3DMWeb_Share%26utm_campaign%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%252Frealtimenews%252Farticle%252Fnew%252F20170928%252F1212655%252F&d=OigZPHgmmXLSVwsZB9mDHb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=463d008e\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20170928/1212655/?utm_source=FB&amp;utm_medium=MWeb_Share&amp;utm_campaign=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Fnew%2F20170928%2F1212655%2F</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6b5848b02edac9187e35058ba2d3eaede3f8c99","tid":417161,"uid":46231,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:52:48.000Z","msg":"見親三星都淨係識講爆炸果班idog可唔可以出黎回應一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86ebebba666bdbe0cf6026a75b43e8993768e426","tid":417161,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:56:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uf0h2ls6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuf0h2ls6&h=a1adb594&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只用3天的全新iPhone 8 Plus 手機，在充電時突然爆裂。洪舜南攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lc8f0rha\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flc8f0rha&h=d3c4d7fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n吳小姐的iPhone 8 Plus (上)不明原因出現電池膨脹，導致手機爆裂。洪舜南攝<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/hrcb74a9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fhrcb74a9&h=c0330d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n通訊行老闆娘董小姐說，開店這麼久第一次遇到iPhone出現電池膨脹導致手機爆裂的狀況。洪舜南攝"},{"pid":"e72abd4a8921113f023eb662a76644d60fd871a3","tid":417161,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T11:59:51.000Z","msg":"無得炒 仲要爆開埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a607baee36446c537ca41eda1a2a080c4da61a","tid":417161,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:01:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b085742c5ff2348f25391072f158f5c16b223101","tid":417161,"uid":32399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28T12:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見親三星都淨係識講爆炸果班idog可唔可以出黎回應一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n威力唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲上到飛機"},{"pid":"d832e3025346c4d6503ef6a8c9782950df2edbea","tid":417161,"uid":46231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-28